components.text: [b][color=#000000][size=21] EDI: How many orders are processed using electronic data interchange? What potential is untapped?[/size][/color][/b]
[size=15][b][color=#000000]  Identify suppliers with high transactional volume but low e-business rate and heavily reduce throughput times caused by manual efforts in the process.[/color][/b][/size]

formulas.name: Savings per Year
formulas.text:
--edi ratio difference
(<%= EDI_TRGT %>/100.0
-
--edi actual ratio
(SUM(CASE 
WHEN "NAST"."NACHA" IN ('6','9','A') AND ISNULL("NAST"."DATVR")=0 AND NAST.KSCHL NOT IN ('MAHN','AUFB') AND NAST.AENDE <> 'X' THEN 1.0
WHEN ISNULL(NAST.DATVR)=1 THEN 0.0
ELSE 0.0 END)
/
SUM(CASE 
WHEN ISNULL("NAST"."DATVR")=0 AND NAST.KSCHL NOT IN ('MAHN','AUFB') AND NAST.AENDE <> 'X' THEN 1.0
WHEN ISNULL(NAST.DATVR)=1 THEN 0.0
ELSE 0.0 END))
)

--times sales orders
*
COUNT_TABLE("EKKO")

--times saving per sales order when processed via EDI
*
<%=EDI_SAVINGS%>

--times FTE COST PER MINUTE
*
(<%= FTE_COST %>/(<%= FTE_HOURS %>*60.0))
